  fixing python 3.2 tests for bug 450666

  06 Jan 2013; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> hgtools-2.0.2.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Clean up the ebuild. Add a dep on mercurial, and use-deps on other Python
